<span id="Description"></span>
== Описание ==

Эта команда позволяет поместить текстовый блок на [[Drawing Landscape A3/ru|чертёжный лист]].

<span id="Usage"></span>
<div class="mw-translate-fuzzy">
== Использование ==
</div>

# Create a [[Drawing Landscape A3|Drawing page]]
# [[Std_Refresh|Refresh]] the view if a Drawing view wasn't opened
# Press the {{KEY|[[Image:Drawing Annotation.png|16px]] [[Drawing Annotation|Drawing Annotation]]}} button
# Adjust the desired properties, such as text contents, font, size and position.

